abstract: State Dept decries killing of Luis Diaz, local opposition leader in Venezuela's Guarico State, who was shot at public meeting days before legislative election; urges Venezuelan government to protect all political candidates.
lead_paragraph: The local activist, Luis Díaz, a leader of the opposition Democratic Action party in Guárico State, was shot at a public meeting on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: The Americas; Venezuela: U.S. Condemns a Killing
